
Steps for connecting to local MySQL dB:

1. Add the following 2 lines in your settings.py and __init__.py 

import pymysql
pymysql.install_as_MySQLdb()

2. Navigate inside your Virtual Environment to this path: \myvenv\Lib\site-packages\django\db\backends\mysql

In operations.py, search for "decode" and replace it with "encode"
In base.py, search for "version < (1, 3, 13):" and comment the code snippet inside if

3. Save all the files, activate your virtual environment and cd inside BinManagementProject and run the following commands:

pip install wheel
pip install pymysql